\end{verbatim}

We need to create the following conjunction:

\begin{verbatim}
    (C1 or C3) and (C1 or C4) and (C1 or C5) and (C1 or C6)
and (C2 or C3) and (C2 or C4) and (C2 or C5) and (C2 or C6)
and (C3 or C6) and (C4 or C6) and (C5 or C6)
